sentence: what northwest flights leave denver before noon
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', '"'||v0.airline_code||'"',
 '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 v0.departure_time FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2 
WHERE ((v0.airline_code = 'NW') AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code)
